{"type": "article", "id": 39739, "title": "留个纪念吧，把你惦记的城市戴在身上｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-04-12T23:18:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 9999, "name": "Flos"}, {"id": 39455, "name": "Art. Lebedev Studio"}, {"id": 39456, "name": "NastPlas"}, {"id": 247, "name": "Nendo"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 338, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170412225028MYgLd739JSBTvq4O.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>You Are Here by Talia Sari</h3><p>最让你魂萦梦绕的地点是什么？故乡、某次旅行的目的地、还是那个第一次鼓足勇气吻向心爱之人的小巷？<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/TaliaSari\" rel=\"nofollow\">Talia Sari</a> 是一名现居美国纽约的工业设计师兼珠宝匠，远离故乡的她在过去六年的时间里为同样“心有所属”的人们定制了根据某地的地图所打造的各类首饰，并将这个系列命名为 “You Are Here”。只要在专属的定制页面上输入地址，独一无二的街道就会被精准地转换成错综复杂的几何线条，成为一件充满回忆的贴身饰品。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1453024882/you-are-here-your-personal-map-jewelry\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价从 99 美元起，有 24K 镀金和镀银两种版本可选。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170412225113mrG6lcP3qgjSspbf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170412225111ko9QhyKFV7XB12YP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.669231\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170412225111OeGb8Ca26A4VZizl.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170412225111zCtIZsgGvnK3RMWN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170412225112xq0wN7zjAtVpIrMb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Gaku by nendo</h3><p>在今年的米兰设计周上，日本设计公司 <a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">nendo</a> 为意大利灯具品牌 <a href=\"http://www.flos.com/en/home\" rel=\"nofollow\">Flos</a> 打造的模块化箱子 Gaku 或许会让你想到“一窗一世界”这样的概念。依靠磁力吸附各类配件的 Gaku 就像是一个包罗万象的画框，允许人们发挥创意自由组合。箱子本身还包含了为灯具供电的充电座，由所在的位置来决定灯光是否点亮，进一步强调了互动感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201704122251350hqR1Zipd6fsxQye.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201704122251357V38ITthMqOxuRdk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170412225135aqYOLQf9Cm4Gwt25.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170412225135uHbME6NyIRwXsBGv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170412225135vShxdWcgD34QZeU5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Imagiro carpet by Wayon</h3><p>既然餐巾能够叠成一朵漂亮的花、酒店里的毛巾可以变成一只小动物，为什么不让地毯也能玩出各种花样呢？米兰设计周期间，西班牙 EINA 设计大学的学生团队 Wayon 就带来了这张可以折的地毯 Imagiro ，打破了“地毯必须平整”这一刻板印象。如果你心灵手巧的话，只要加上一些固定用的零件，就能用放大版的折纸作品装饰你的房间了。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170412225153sXwxUCPz5gpoaqTK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663810\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201704122251539cFAYBPUqkgysCl1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663810\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170412225152fEaHmP3xu0tiNJQ6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663810\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201704122251520H1SjnJKI5zgivfA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663810\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170412225152hUjQI8MOLvlpbZid.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.239048\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Numizmatus money box by Art. Lebedev Studio</h3><p>结束一段异国之旅，你会不会留一枚当地的硬币做纪念？为了帮助人们大大方方地展示这些体积较小的藏品，俄罗斯设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.artlebedev.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Art. Lebedev Studio</a> 带来了这款名为 Numizmatus 的储蓄工具。强调装饰性的它并没有采用常见的罐头造型，反而更像是一个不断更新的相框。借助细缝，投入的硬币也不会彼此遮挡，让人更有动力将整个画框填满。目前 Numizmatus 还处于概念阶段，尚未投入生产。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170412225314o897ilIxT3zMRqbN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666154\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170412225314r9j0Pey1blkfY8oc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.843077\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201704122253133CQynN2PgYjiT0DM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666154\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170412225314hPAf3LXx0q4NBbMO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.140000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Rainy Seasons by Pavla Chuykina</h3><p>春天来临，不少地方的雨水也变多了。为了体现雨水为蔬果生长所作的贡献，俄罗斯包装设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/Pavla\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pavla Chuykina</a> 特意打造了这个名为 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/50530929/Rainy-Seasons-Herbs-Vegetables\" rel=\"nofollow\">Rainy Seasons</a> 的概念蔬果品牌。借鉴“燕子低飞必下雨”这句谚语而设计的 logo 结合了水滴和燕子的形象，而装蔬果的容器也被改造成了透明的雨伞，除了靠近顶端的标签之外并没有其他装饰，营造出一种格外清爽的感觉。和普通的塑料盒相比，你是不是更想带着这把伞离开超市呢？</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170412225209w1Rtsz2hEf68lCSH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.576667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170412225209a9zUEkuDFG70cNbl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.728333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170412225209iCDmYExahBNRXIc1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.609167\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170412225209Z4F0TP7jl6xAza5D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414167\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170412225209YHwBLSKkP0Qal3rO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.537500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>QUO by NastPlas</h3><p>你有没有想象过挥舞画笔后颜料停留在半空中会是怎样的场景？最近，西班牙工作室 <a href=\"http://www.nastplas.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">NastPlas</a> 通过数码渲染让往往停留在平面的油画也变得立体起来。当你仔细观察这套名为 QUO 的作品，会发现看似毫无章法拼接在一起的各色颜料其实巧妙地构成了人或马的头部，而某些比较厚重的部分还会让人联想到织物的质感，忍不住想伸手触碰。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170412225234leKByXPodintzEAM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.622249\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170412225234216savcRWYydwiM9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.628362\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201704122252352jhNecRBEQsXqt5k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.623472\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170412225234Z3EYAwFHDfCcQ0SU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.839853\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170412225235Dj0QH7z6sMx9qe83.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.841076\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}